{"word":"πώγων","slug":"πώγων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πώγων</b></el> <el>(πώγων, ωνος, ὁ,) </el><p/><i>the beard</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—<a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>πώγων πυρός</el> <i>a beard</i> or <i>tail</i> of fire, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/>"}]}